data.description: Spacious, well-maintained blond bungalow near excellent transportation with side drive.  The extra wide porch opens up to beautiful hardwood flooring, tray ceilings, lots of natural light.  Kitchen has granite counters and beautiful 42" cabinets.  The kitchen extends into space that can be used as a den or additional dining.  Spacious basement is already finished and perfect for entertaining.  2nd floor features a beautiful, master suite.
